<h1 id="toc7"><span>事件报告</span></h1>
</div>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="https://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-cn-1866/PP]Y6PC}YN4F__85CK6313C.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="PP]Y6PC}YN4F__85CK6313C.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
